        "tokensBefore": 175085,
        "tokensAfter": 11117,
        "summary": "## Goal\nJoin the **AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe / Phúc An)** project and read all requirements and project description from Confluence and GitLab via MCP.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Only use **Confluence space `OTLXPA1`** for DTLX project docs (space `AW` is for AHV WORKS — do not use)\n- Use GitLab repos: `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (id: 81078323) and `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (id: 81078350)\n- Use local workspace: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/` and `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/`\n- Delete all AHV WORKS data from memory\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Confirmed confluence-dtlx MCP server is operational and accessible\n- [x] Verified access to Confluence spaces `OTLXPA1` (Đào tạo lái xe - Phúc An) and `AW` (AHV Work)\n- [x] Read full ERD from Confluence page id `23494657` (\"ERD và tài liệu mô tả sản phẩm đào tạo lái xe\", version 35) — 20+ entities documented\n- [x] Read Dashboard spec (page id `66394`, v3)\n- [x] Read Quản lý Leads spec (page id `98387`, v12)\n- [x] Read Quản lý Học viên spec (page id `589834`, v5)\n- [x] Identified all Confluence pages in OTLXPA1 space (~20+ pages covering all modules)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Reading remaining Confluence pages for full project requirements\n\n### Blocked\n- GitLab README files inaccessible via `gitlab_get_file` (JSON parse error on `#` markdown header) and `web_fetch` (403 Cloudflare)\n- Confluence search for driving training docs returned no results under wrong space `AW`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Used wrong Confluence space initially**: Assistant first searched space `AW` and found only AHV WORKS docs (ERD, leave management, new features). User clarified this is a separate driving training project.\n- **User provided correct context**: After clarification failure, user provided full project context including correct Confluence space (`OTLXPA1`), GitLab repo IDs, and local workspace paths.\n- **AHV DTLX is the driving school management system** (Đào Tạo Lái Xe), NOT AHV WORKS. Must not confuse the two.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Read remaining key Confluence pages (courses, teachers, lessons, exams, vehicles, payments, sales, app sale, etc.)\n2. Read GitLab MR descriptions for project requirements and context\n3. Map ERD entities to the codebase in local workspace\n4. Await task assignment from Khương Nịnh\n\n## Critical Context\n- **GitLab repos**: `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (81078323), `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (81078350), `ahv-dtlx/ahv-landing-page-v2` (80400174)\n- **Confluence space**: `OTLXPA1` — contains ERD + ~20 module specs\n- **ERD (page `23494657`, v35)**: 20+ entities including `User`, `Roles`, `UserRole`, `StudentInfos`, `Stadiums`, `LeadSources`, `LeadInfos`, `Courses`, `LicenseCategories` (A1/A2/B1/B2/C...), `CourseStudent`, `Lessons`, `LessonTypes`, `Vehicles`, `TeacherInfo`, `TeacherLicenseCategory`, `WorkCalenders`, `Exams`, `ExamResults`, `Payments`, `VehicleCost`, `Guest`, `Notifies`\n- **System flow**: Lead → Sales → Course enrollment → Lessons (theory/cabin/practical) → Exam → License\n- **Local workspace paths**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/` and `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/`\n- **User**: Khương Nịnh (khuowgn, id: 6053576134), project owner and collaborator",
        "firstKeptEntryId": "22f5f117",
        "preCompaction": {
          "sessionId": "b90d0cbf-72bc-4ccf-b0a9-5bf84f42e416",
